01:09:49.360 --> 01:10:02.620 align:middle line:90%


01:10:02.620 --> 01:10:09.460 align:middle line:84%
>> All of us have changed in the
time since 4'33" was first made

01:10:09.460 --> 01:10:10.300 align:middle line:90%
in the early '50s.

01:10:10.300 --> 01:10:14.070 align:middle line:90%


01:10:14.070 --> 01:10:19.070 align:middle line:84%
