01:11:56.320 --> 01:12:00.910 align:middle line:84%
Four minutes and 33 seconds of
meditation in which everyone

01:12:00.910 --> 01:12:01.900 align:middle line:90%
is silent together.

01:12:01.900 --> 01:12:04.940 align:middle line:90%


01:12:04.940 --> 01:12:08.990 align:middle line:84%
It's the most extraordinary
