01:12:14.690 --> 01:12:16.490 align:middle line:84%
to absolutely
everything that happens.

01:12:16.490 --> 01:12:19.020 align:middle line:90%


01:12:19.020 --> 01:12:21.500 align:middle line:84%
You just sense this
breathing organism

01:12:21.500 --> 01:12:24.038 align:middle line:84%
of people in this place
during this moment.

01:12:24.038 --> 01:12:27.026 align:middle line:90%


01:12:27.026 --> 01:12:30.014 align:middle line:90%
[APPLAUSE]

01:12:30.014 --> 01:12:39.974 align:middle line:90%


01:12:39.974 --> 01:12:42.464 align:middle line:10%
>> Well, that's one of the
