01:12:46.448 --> 01:12:50.432 align:middle line:90%
4'33" by John Cage.

01:12:50.432 --> 01:13:48.900 align:middle line:90%


01:13:48.900 --> 01:13:49.700 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

01:13:49.700 --> 01:13:51.620 align:middle line:84%
>> If we could all learn
